  "texts": [
    "Finally, we evaluated Lingo3DMol on the Directory of Useful Decoys-Enhanced (DUD-E) dataset and compared it with state-of-the-art (SOTA) methods.",
    "Lingo3DMol outperformed existing methods on various metrics.",
    "Our main contributions can be summarized as follows:",
    "• A new FSMILES molecule representation that incorporates both local and global coordinates is introduced, enabling the generation of 3D molecules with reasonable 3D conformations and two-dimensional (2D) topology.",
    "• A 3D molecule denoising pretraining method and an independent NCI/anchor model are developed to help overcome the problem of limited data and identify potential NCI binding sites."
